<h1><span style="font-weight: 400;">Vidar Stealer – the attacker&#8217;s perspective</span></h1>
<h2><b>Executive summary:</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Vidar stealer is a malware that is offered for sale in the MAAS (Malware as a service) model.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is present since 2018, and it is a variant of the “Arkei stealer”.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br />
</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Vidar is currently one of the top stealers that are available for sale and is responsible for a large sum of compromised credentials offered for sale on underground forums and marketplaces.</span></p>
